<li> Words cannot express the sorrow I feel for your family.  Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li> Your family is in my heart during this difficult time.  May precious memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li> I am so deeply saddened by the news of your loss.  May peace find you soon.</li>
<li> Sending you strength and love as you navigate this heartbreaking journey.</li>
<li> May the memories of your loved one bring you comfort and solace in the days ahead.</li>
<li> With heartfelt sympathy, I offer my condolences to your family during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li> Please accept my deepest sympathies.  May you find peace amidst your grief.</li>
<li> Thinking of your family and sending heartfelt condolences.</li>
<li> Your loss is deeply felt.  May the love surrounding you bring some comfort.</li>
<li> I was so saddened to hear of your loss.  My heart goes out to your family.</li>
<li> I offer my sincerest condolences on the passing of your beloved.  May their memory be a blessing.</li>
<li> My thoughts and prayers are with your family during this painful time.</li>
<li> Sending my love and deepest condolences to you and your family. May you find strength in each other.</li>
<li> Please know that I am here for you and your family in any way you need.</li>
    

